Name: Patricia Dierser
Review: I'm absolutely thrilled with this charger! It has revolutionized my nightstand setup by occupying minimal space and doubling as a convenient phone stand that resembles an alarm clock. This design choice makes it effortless to keep an eye on my phone's screen. The thoughtful angle at which it holds my phone is a game changer, allowing me to charge and stream content simultaneously - a feature that truly enhances my experience.

Name: Chandira
Review_title: About the only flat chargers that have worked with my iphone
Review:
I have bought several versions of these that haven't worked. I'm happy that they work!! My iPhone Jack has failed, so these are the only means I have of charging my phone now. They're quite slow, but better than nothing.
I wish the cord was longer.

Name: J. P. Reader
Review: We have these next to the bed to charge our phones overnight. That part works great. However, the green light to tell you that the phone is charging is so bright it lights up half of the room. I put a piece of blue painters tape over the light and it is still so bright I could almost read by it. Electrical tape will be next.

Name: Gerald harper
Review: Stopped plugging in charger, ruined almost every phone I ever owned. Works great. thinking about getting to more.

Name: E. Southcott
Review: They work as they say they will. Good price.

Name: Jetter
Review: Charges as expected... but once your device is full, it will not keep it charged; you have to remove your phone from the charger and put it back on in order to charge it back up. So at night, when your phone reaches 100% around midnight, it will slowly discharge and be a 90% when you wake up.

Name: Dvd
Review:
This charger does work for my iPhone 12 and iPhone 10. It isn't too fussy about placement but if it is moved slightly it can stop charging which can be a problem if you touch your phone during an overnight charging.
I did purchase two more. I haven't had the problems others have reported such dying after limited usage, getting too hot or giving an incomplete charge. I'd rate it as good value for the money.

Name: Kindle Customer
Review: Ah lak eet!

Name: Amazon Customer
Review: slightly slower charging than the plug in type

Name: Kindle Customer
Review:
Unit does quickly charge device to 100% however once charged to full it turns off charging. Problem is it never turns charging back on unless devices is removed and placed back on
This is a problem when charging at bedtime only to wake up with device not fully charged cause it lost battery life while charging unit automatic turned off at 100%. My phone percentage went from 100 to 85 percent in less than two hours with it on charging while listening to music . Not happy with them at all.

Name: Kimberly D
Review: It works well for my iPhone 13. It charges fast. The trick is to place it on the charger correctly. I think the ones complaining about it not working are not placing it on the charger properly. I love the black color and the light is unobtrusive but I can still tell when it is charging. These are wonderful!

Name: Peter R.
Review: Just make sure you know what side is up! LOL

Name: AmyCabo
Review:
So easy to use!!!!
But does not work with all phones. And won't work with some cases. So do your research

Name: Fluff
Review:
I purchased these to have multiple wireless charges in multiple locations...1 in office and 1 next to bed. They did not have the Fast charging capability or charge my Samsung Galaxy Earbuds to full capacity. It took hours to charge my phone and did not work through the case I had on my phone.

The case was just a cheap little plastic thing that I've had for years and the charging capability did not penetrate.

They DID charge, just not as advertised hence the 3 out 5 rating.

These items were returned.

Return process was easy as pie though!

Name: RJ
Review: Works perfectly as advertised. Make sure you use a fast charging usb wall adapter for the full fast charging experience. Charged my iphone 13 from 30% to 100% in less than 45 minutes. 5 stars.

Name: Michael Jaros
Review: I like the fact that I don't have to use the lightning portal, because mine won't stay in

Name: Caffeine mama
Review: It's good enough for the price I paid, but super slow charge compared to the one that comes with iPhone.

Name: Amazon Customer
Review_title: Small learning curve but great product
Review: I got this charger because I was sick if trying to plug my iPhone cable into my phone past a thick otter box. I would suggest if you are one to watch a lot of YouTube videos you'll want a 10 foot cable. But this works great.

Name: Jorge Fernandez
Review: Hubiera pagado mas , si incluyera el cargador. Debi hacer otra orden y esperar un nuevo envio.

Name: Nic B.
Review: Works just like they should

Name: Exavier
Review: Work great
